Lapidoth-Heletz Has Biggest Two-Day Gain in Month on Rights

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-08-15T11:56:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/lapidoth-heletz-has-biggest-two-day-gain-in-month-on-rights.html
Lapidoth-Heletz LP had its biggest
two-day gain in more than a month in  Tel Aviv  after the Israeli
government lifted a warning that the company may lose drilling
rights at its Heletz 41 site.  Lapidoth rose as much as 13.5 percent, the most since July
11, and was trading at 0.15 shekel at 2:12 p.m. in Tel Aviv.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Jerusalem at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net . 